title: UCB FSF
description: My coursework from UC Berkeley in case you'd like to learn how to code from the ground up to the MERN stack.

body.raw:
# My Class Repository

Welcome to my class repository! This repository contains various files related to my class assignments, projects, and materials.

## Files

- [00-Admin-Resources](https://github.com/jbxamora/myclassrepo/tree/main/00-admin-resources) (initial commit, 8 months ago)
  
- [01-HTML-Git-CSS](https://github.com/jbxamora/myclassrepo/tree/main/01-html-git-css) (updated state folder 2 months ago)

- [02-Advanced-CSS](https://github.com/jbxamora/myclassrepo/tree/main/02-Advanced-CSS) (advanced CSS, 4 months ago)

- [03-JavaScript](https://github.com/jbxamora/myclassrepo/tree/main/03-JavaScript) (JavaScript, 4 months ago)

- [04-Web-APIs](https://github.com/jbxamora/myclassrepo/tree/main/04-Web-APIs) (web APIs, 4 months ago)

- [05-Third-Party-APIs](https://github.com/jbxamora/myclassrepo/tree/main/05-Third-Party-APIs) (third-party APIs, 4 months ago)

- [06-Server-Side-APIs](https://github.com/jbxamora/myclassrepo/tree/main/06-Server-Side-APIs) (server-side APIs, 4 months ago)

- [07-Project-1](https://github.com/jbxamora/myclassrepo/tree/main/07-Project-1) (updated state folder 2 months ago)

- [08-NodeJS](https://github.com/jbxamora/myclassrepo/tree/main/08-NodeJS) (Node.js, 4 months ago)

- [09-OOP](https://github.com/jbxamora/myclassrepo/tree/main/09-OOP) (OOP, 4 months ago)

- [10-Express](https://github.com/jbxamora/myclassrepo/tree/main/10-Express) (Express, 4 months ago)

- [11-SQL](https://github.com/jbxamora/myclassrepo/tree/main/11-SQL) (SQL, 4 months ago)

- [12-ORM](https://github.com/jbxamora/myclassrepo/tree/main/12-ORM) (ORM, 4 months ago)

- [13-MVC](https://github.com/jbxamora/myclassrepo/tree/main/13-MVC) (MVC, 4 months ago)

- [14-Project-2](https://github.com/jbxamora/myclassrepo/tree/main/14-Project-2) (updated state folder 2 months ago)

- [15-Computer-Science](https://github.com/jbxamora/myclassrepo/tree/main/15-Computer%20Science) (computer science, 4 months ago)

- [16-NoSQL](https://github.com/jbxamora/myclassrepo/tree/main/16-NoSQL) (updated to current module - PWA, 3 months ago)

- [17-PWA](https://github.com/jbxamora/myclassrepo/tree/main/17-PWA) (updated PWA, 3 months ago)

- [18-React](https://github.com/jbxamora/myclassrepo/tree/main/18-React) (added MERN module, 3 months ago)

- [19-MERN](https://github.com/jbxamora/myclassrepo/tree/main/19-MERN) (added solutions for MERN activities and added final module 'state/redux', 3 months ago)

- [20-State](https://github.com/jbxamora/myclassrepo/tree/main/20-State) (updated state folder, 2 months ago)
